{"tid":1548251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北角碼頭現浮屍　男死者雙手被綁起身綁4塊磚頭","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T07:07:21.000Z","uid":314180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f9860f620a0191d8eec49b1b5fb90f82823a289f","tid":1548251,"uid":314180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"北角碼頭對出海面今早發現浮屍。救援人員打撈起男子後，當場證實不治，警方發現死者雙手被綁起，認為事件有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n早上約8時許，有市民在北角碼頭發現海面有疑似男子倒插於水中，載浮載沉，於是報警求助。救援人員到場後把一名年長男子救起，當場證實男子經已不治。警方到場調查，發現死者雙手被綁起，其身上綁住一個黑色環保袋，環保袋內有一個膠籃，內有4塊磚頭。警方認為事件有可疑，並用帳篷將屍體遮蓋，刑事偵緝探員在場展開調查，目前正調查死者身分及死因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2446737/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2446737%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b44bf783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2446737/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n點解呢兩個月發生呢一類事情？非法處理屍體？"},{"pid":"2b0abaf3ad041b33099920b2fbadec34a3b7bfa6","tid":1548251,"uid":67074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=31c5b422\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到要<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復</strong></span>這<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港</strong></span><br />\n同行兒女為正義<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>時代革命</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.